{"tid":94336,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"(hardrock撚）有無人有聽開Aerosmith","createTime":"2017-01-25T06:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T16:56:06.000Z","uid":69486,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"817fafe20dbec065e1fa6f179614ab0017023777","tid":94336,"uid":69486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:54:18.000Z","msg":"Aerosmith,一隊黎自美國Boston 嘅老牌blue-based hardrock band<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 1970 年成立，成立初期成員換過幾次，最後成員名單係：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/140759_195fdf31bb83b3618f64eabbe7ced115.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F140759_195fdf31bb83b3618f64eabbe7ced115.jpg&h=8745cfc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左起：結他手 Joe Perry,Bass 手 Tom Hamilton,主音Steven Tyler, 鼓手 Joey Kramer同結他手 Brad Whitford.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95e4Jk9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95e4Jk9.jpg&h=af06b2d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然而家變曬阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但越老越有味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拎過四次格林美獎，2001年入左搖滾名人堂 (Rock&amp;roll Hall of Fame), 總共出過15隻album,<br />\n而係1998年佢哋為絕世天劫（Armageddon) 依套戲唱左首主題曲，亦為依首歌出左佢哋第一隻single, ' I don't want to miss a thing'<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JkK8g6FMEXE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJkK8g6FMEXE&d=o63dqAD8vxmsRe%2FP1KBI0wv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=1961e854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JkK8g6FMEXE</a><br />\n我諗有唔少人第一次聽Aerosmith 都應該係聽依首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時最後一隻Album 係2012 出嘅 'Music from Another Dimension!'<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UKW77Y5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUKW77Y5.jpg&h=7c13e149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人推介依首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rDZ1QzejZ78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrDZ1QzejZ78&d=o63dqAD8vxmsRe%2FP1KBI0wv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=ad6dbbf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rDZ1QzejZ78</a><br />\n<br />\nAerosmith 嘅歌，我個人黎講覺得有兩種好極端嘅感覺，一係就充滿陽剛味，但又不失細膩，一種鐵漢柔情嘅感覺，例如依首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d7lCZ0rpH3o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd7lCZ0rpH3o&d=o63dqAD8vxmsRe%2FP1KBI0wv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=b5286927\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d7lCZ0rpH3o</a><br />\n<br />\n另一種就係有種比較調皮，玩味比較重嘅歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZfbBqBOSXlU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZfbBqBOSXlU&d=o63dqAD8vxmsRe%2FP1KBI0wv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=af56d065\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZfbBqBOSXlU</a><br />\n<br />\n唔係講笑，Steven Tyler 嘅音域真係癡撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依段係佢之前自己一個上American Idol 表演嘅live<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q61vIK9RTPU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQ61vIK9RTPU&d=o63dqAD8vxmsRe%2FP1KBI0wv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=13c065ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Q61vIK9RTPU</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>有無同好</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32641bfbda48a5dec02025e14308efb01281b899","tid":94336,"uid":277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:27:05.000Z","msg":"What could have been love🤘🏿"},{"pid":"e97a0ced28a5d4e46f3ae2ff10da56604152e8b0","tid":94336,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:29:16.000Z","msg":"只係聽過 i dun wanna miss a thing"},{"pid":"e83f686ab0d7b02e69f8b8095650de07536bdfb4","tid":94336,"uid":31172,"like":0,"dislike":